defaultwe have 
defaultsubmitted 
defaultto HMRC to da
defaultte.
default  We do not believe that the
default 
defaultguidance take
defaults
default account of the wide variety of different commercial arrangements many firms have agreed within their partner group.
default  In addition, the guidance does not cover any of the practical issues which will arise for LLPs in applying the new legislation such as the amounts upon which PAYE and NIC must be paid or the interaction with for example the overlap rules for members who 
defaultare now treated as salaried members.
default17
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultWe believe that, once changes and improvements have been made to the legislation, the guidance should be rewritten to reflect the revised legislation, taking account of a far wider range of commercial arrangements.
